TWComponent.script: tw.local.sqlStatement select TM.MONITOR_NAME || ' - ' || TM.MONITOR_SEQ as monitor , trunc(TMR.CHECK_DATETIME,'hh24') + (trunc(to_char(TMR.CHECK_DATETIME,'mi')))/24/60 + (trunc(to_char(TMR.CHECK_DATETIME,'ss')/60)*60)/24/60/60 as name, TRUNC(avg(TMR.RESPONSE_TIME), 3) from TDSH_MONITOR_RESULTS TMR, TDSH_MONITORS TM where TM.MONITOR_SEQ = TMR.MONITOR_SEQ and TM.MONITOR_TYPE_ID = 1 and TMR.CHECK_DATETIME > SYSDATE -120/1440 group by TM.MONITOR_NAME || ' - ' || TM.MONITOR_SEQ , trunc(TMR.CHECK_DATETIME,'hh24') + (trunc(to_char(TMR.CHECK_DATETIME,'mi')))/24/60 + (trunc(to_char(TMR.CHECK_DATETIME,'ss')/60)*60)/24/60/60 order by name
